==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blackbirding
<hw>Black"bird*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The kidnapping
of negroes or Polynesians to be sold as slaves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act or practice of collecting natives of the
islands near Queensland for service on the Queensland sugar
plantations.</def> <mark>[Australia]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blackboard</ent>⟦br⟧
